name: Liquity V2
description: Liquity V2 is a decentralized and immutable borrowing protocol that allows you to set your own interest rate and draw loans against ETH, wstETH and rETH.

methodology.Fees: Total interest, redemption fees paid by borrowers and liquidation gas compensate.
methodology.Revenue: 25% of borrow interests are collected as protocol liquidity incentives.
methodology.SupplySideRevenue: 75% of borrow interests to stability pools takers, all redemption fees paid to borrowers and all gas compensations to liquidators.

Fees.Gas Compensation: Gas compensations paid to liquidator when trigger liquidations.

Revenue.Protocol Incentivized Liquidity: 25% of borrow interests collected as protocol liquidity incentives.

SupplySideRevenue.Borrow Interest To Stability Pools: 75% of borrow interests to stability pools stakers.
SupplySideRevenue.Redemtion Fee To Borrowers: All redemtion fees are distributed to borrowers.
SupplySideRevenue.Gas Compensation: All gas compensations paid to liquidator when trigger liquidations.
